OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud mostly clearing
OL,6,Fbut patches may linger near western
OL,7,Fcoasts, and generally remaining
OL,8,Fcloudier and breezier for northwest
OL,9,FScotland with patchy rain. Elsewhere,
OL,10,Fa hot day with prolonged periods of
OL,11,Fsunshine, albeit hazy at times.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud and rain remains across
OL,14,Fnorthwest Scotland. Otherwise, dry and
OL,15,Flargely clear, though low cloud and
OL,16,Ffog pushing inland again into parts of
OL,17,Fthe west. A warm night for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
