OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FRain in the northwest may turn
OL,6,Fheavy for a time. The small chance of
OL,7,Fa shower developing elsewhere, but
OL,8,Fmany once again staying dry and
OL,9,Fpredominantly sunny. Another hot day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
